===Etymology===
{{etyl|la}} [[ad]] [[locum]] - at the place

===Adverb===
'''ad loc.'''

# [[there|There]], [[at]] the specified [[location]]

====Usage notes====
This term is used in a citation to a commentary to indicate that the location in the commentary at which the cited reference can be found is at the place under discussion.

